OL,3,CFarmers call for inheritance tax U-
OL,4,Cturn ahead of talks with ministers
OL,6,FReversing plans to charge inheritance
OL,7,Ftax on farms is "the only sensible
OL,8,Fcourse of action", the head of the
OL,9,FNational Farmers' Union has said.
OL,11,FNFU president Tom Bradshaw is to meet
OL,12,Fthe Environment Secretary Steve Reed
OL,13,Fon Monday amid growing anger over the
OL,14,Fchancellor's decision to make farms
OL,15,Fsubject to inheritance tax.
