OL,3,CFarmers call for inheritance tax U-
OL,4,Cturn ahead of talks with ministers
OL,6,FUnder plans announced in the Budget,
OL,7,Finheritance tax will be charged at 20%
OL,8,Fon farms worth more than #1 million,
OL,9,Falthough the chancellor has said in
OL,10,Fsome cases the threshold could in
OL,11,Fpractice be around #3 million.
OL,13,FBut writing in the Daily Telegraph, Mr
OL,14,FBradshaw said the prospect of being
OL,15,Funable to pass their businesses on to
OL,16,Ftheir children would be "the final
OL,17,Fstraw" for many farmers.
