OL,6,FHe said: "The vast majority of the
OL,7,Fpeople who will bear the brunt of this
OL,8,Fdecision aren't wealthy people with
OL,9,Fhuge cash reserves hidden away.
OL,11,F"They are families that have often
OL,12,Fspent generations building up their
OL,13,Ffarm businesses to provide food for
OL,14,Fthe nation, often on very tight profit
OL,15,Fmargins.
