OL,3,CFarmers call for inheritance tax U-
OL,4,Cturn ahead of talks with ministers
OL,6,F"Their businesses have struggled
OL,7,Fthrough all the changes caused by
OL,8,FBrexit, they've suffered years of
OL,9,Fbeing squeezed to the lowest margins
OL,10,Fimaginable, with costs of production
OL,11,Fskyrocketing, they've been battered by
OL,12,Fincreasingly extreme weather
OL,13,Fconditions. They have nothing left to
OL,14,Fgive."
OL,16,FTax experts have suggested the changes
OL,17,Fcould affect fewer than 500 farms a
OL,18,Fyear, once the tax thresholds and
OL,19,Ffarmers giving their property to their
OL,20,Fchildren before they die are taken
OL,21,Finto account.
