OL,4,Cturn ahead of talks with ministers
OL,6,FBut Mr Bradshaw said the Treasury had
OL,7,Fa "completely skewed view of the
OL,8,Fstructure of farming in the UK".
OL,10,FHe said: "Very few viable farms are
OL,11,Fworth under #1 million. That could buy
OL,12,Fyou 50 acres and a house today. No
OL,13,Fviable food-producing business is 50
OL,14,Facres. The average farm in the UK is
OL,15,Fmore than 250 acres.
