OL,3,CFarmers call for inheritance tax U-
OL,4,Cturn ahead of talks with ministers
OL,6,F"The only sensible course of action
OL,7,Ffor the future of family farms across
OL,8,Fthe country, as well as for the sake
OL,9,Fof Britain's food security and our
OL,10,Flegislated environmental targets, is
OL,11,Fto reverse this decision."
OL,13,FChancellor Rachel Reeves has defended
OL,14,Fher proposed reforms, saying it is not
OL,15,F"affordable" to keep the current
OL,16,Fsystem.
