OL,3,CFarmers call for inheritance tax U-
OL,4,Cturn ahead of talks with ministers
OL,6,FSpeaking on the BBC's Sunday With
OL,7,FLaura Kuenssberg, Reeves said: "Only a
OL,8,Fvery small number of agricultural
OL,9,Fproperties will be affected, but last
OL,10,Fyear the benefits of agricultural
OL,11,Fproperty relief, 40% of the benefit
OL,12,Fwas felt by 7% of the wealthiest land
OL,13,Fowners.
OL,15,F"I don't think it is affordable to
OL,16,Fcarry on with a relief like that when
OL,17,Four public finances are under so much
OL,18,Fpressure."
